as/10e2a90ecd65720a46b7fde6524cf054.poster.avif?t=1750073868\" width=626 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1639080/extras/10e2a90ecd65720a46b7fde6524cf054.webm?t=1750073868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make choices that will affect your future expeditions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character has different powers. It's up to you to explore lost ruins as an archaeologist or to track down massive creatures as a hunter. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't underestimate the weather! It conditions the movements of caravanners and the outcome of confrontations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repair the broken climate, and put an end to centuries of wandering.</p></li></ul>",
